Microarray T-cell acitivation

Tcells.Rd

A data set with 44 replications of four genes involved in T-cells activation. For each gene there are ten repeated measurements recorded at 0, 2, 4, 6, 8, 18, 24, 32, 48, 72 hours after the treatement.

Tcells

Format

A data frame with 44 rows and 40 columns.

rows

independent and identical replications.

FYB.0

expression levels for gene FYB at the time of treatment.

CD69.0

expression levels for CD 69 at the time of treatment.

IL2RG.0

expression levels for interleuking gene IL-2Rgamma at the time of treatment.

CDC2.0

expression levels for cyclin A2 gene at the time of treatment.
